data.description: Welcome to your dream home on the Oakhill Golf Course! This stunning residence offers the perfect blend of spacious living, outdoor paradise, and elegant design. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage, this is the ultimate retreat you've been searching for.As you arrive, you'll be immediately captivated by the lush half-acre lot, a true haven for nature enthusiasts and privacy seekers. The well-manicured landscape and the backdrop of the golf course provide a tranquil setting that's second to none.Boasting an impressive 3,326 square feet under the roof, this home offers room to roam and entertain. The crown jewel of the property is undoubtedly the beautiful pool and the screened lanai. Imagine basking in the Florida sun or enjoying a refreshing swim with the serene golf course as your backdrop. The lanai also features an outdoor kitchen area, making it the perfect spot for hosting unforgettable gatherings and barbecues with friends and family.Stepping inside, the home welcomes you with a grand foyer, which opens up to a cozy den, ideal for your home office or library. As you proceed around the corner, you'll discover the inviting living room, complete with a charming fireplace and a cathedral ceiling. Large sliders seamlessly connect the living room to the pool area, creating a perfect indoor-outdoor flow that lets you savor the breathtaking views.For more formal occasions, the separate dining room provides an elegant space for family dinners and special celebrations. The eat-in kitchen is a chef's delight, offering a spacious and well-appointed area to prepare and enjoy your culinary creations.With 3 generously sized bedrooms, including a luxurious master suite, this home ensures a comfortable and private space for every member of the family. The master suite includes a nice sized bathroom which is complete with a soaking tub separate shower and with His and Her sinks provides a serene oasis to unwind after a day on the golf course or by the pool.This home truly has it all - from the ideal location on the 3rd tee box on the Oakhill Golf Course to the spacious layout, outdoor amenities, and elegant interior. It's a rare gem that offers the Florida lifestyle you've been dreaming of. Don't miss your chance to make it yours and experience the epitome of Florida living.Schedule a showing today and prepare to fall in love with your new home on the Oakhill Golf Course!
